    <section class="view" data-view="0">
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="seq">00</span> Workshop</div>
      <h1 class="page">Today's objectives</h1>
      <p class="lede">This workshop will review the current Master of Project Management course structure and curriculum. The session will work through key areas of the degree structure, including unit availability, prerequisite requirements, core and elective options, and opportunities to rationalise or simplify the program.<br><br>The aim of the session is to identify practical changes that could strengthen the MPM structure, curriculum and student experience.</p>
